      "body" : "I realised that using the <code>Stream.of()</code> also returns an unmodifiable list. Took me ages to figure that out. Related: <a href=\"https://stackoverflow.com/questions/2887590/unsupportedoperationexception-on-collection\" title=\"unsupportedoperationexception on collection\">stackoverflow.com/questions/2887590/&hellip;</a>"
