    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 3.0",
    "body" : "<p>Try this!</p>\n\n<pre><code>List&lt;String&gt; x = new ArrayList&lt;String&gt;(Arrays.asList(\"xyz\", \"abc\"));\n</code></pre>\n\n<p>It's a good practice to declare the <code>ArrayList</code> with interface <code>List</code> if you don't have to invoke the specific methods.</p>\n"
