    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 3.0",
    "body" : "<p>The <a href=\"https://github.com/google/guava\" rel=\"noreferrer\">Guava library</a> contains convenience methods for creating lists and other collections which makes this much prettier than using the standard library classes.</p>\n\n<p>Example:</p>\n\n<pre><code>ArrayList&lt;String&gt; list = newArrayList(\"a\", \"b\", \"c\");\n</code></pre>\n\n<p>(This assumes <code>import static com.google.common.collect.Lists.newArrayList;</code>)</p>\n"
